# Expense Tracker Native ğŸ“±ğŸ’°

A modern, feature-rich personal finance management application built with React Native, Expo, and Supabase. Track your expenses and income with advanced security, real-time synchronization, and multilingual support.

## âœ¨ Key Features

- ğŸ“Š **Smart Expense Tracking** - Track income and expenses with custom categories
- ğŸ“ˆ **Data Visualization** - Interactive charts and financial analytics
- ğŸ” **Advanced Security** - Biometric authentication (Face ID/Fingerprint)
- ğŸŒ **Multilingual Support** - English, Chinese Simplified, Chinese Traditional
- â˜ï¸ **Real-time Sync** - Live data updates across all devices
- ğŸ“± **Cross-platform** - iOS, Android, and Web support
- ğŸ¨ **Modern UI** - Beautiful design with dark/light theme support

## ğŸš€ Quick Start

```bash
# Clone and install
git clone <repository-url>
cd expense-tracker-native
npm install

# Setup environment
cp .env.example .env
# Edit .env with your credentials

# Start development
npm start
```

## ğŸ—ï¸ Tech Stack

- **Frontend**: React Native + Expo
- **Backend**: Supabase (PostgreSQL + Auth + Real-time)
- **State Management**: Redux Toolkit
- **UI Components**: Gluestack UI + NativeWind
- **Forms**: React Hook Form + Yup validation
- **Charts**: React Native Gifted Charts
- **Storage**: MMKV for high-performance local storage
- **Internationalization**: react-i18next

